== 芳香环 ==
[[苯基|苯基]]也可稳定碳正离子。下面的反应中，反应物对甲苯磺酸酯在乙酸中发生溶剂解，由于形成了螺三元环中间体，使得正电荷离域到三个位置，较为稳定。接着乙酸分子可以进攻两个环碳中的任意一个，生成两个syn-对映体的混合物。<ref>''Studies in Stereochemistry. I. The Stereospecific Wagner-Meerwein Rearrangement of the Isomers of 3-Phenyl-2-butanol'' [[Donald_J._Cram|Donald J. Cram]] [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]; '''1949'''; 71(12); 3863-3870. [http://pubs.acs.org/cgi-bin/abstract.cgi/jacsat/1949/71/i12/f_ja01180a001.pdf 摘要] {{Wayback|url=http://pubs.acs.org/cgi-bin/abstract.cgi/jacsat/1949/71/i12/f_ja01180a001.pdf |date=20070929124720 }}</ref><ref>''Studies in Stereochemistry. V. Phenonium Sulfonate Ion-pairs as Intermediates in the Intramolecular Rearrangements and Solvolysis Reactions that Occur in the 3-Phenyl-2-butanol System'' [[Donald_J._Cram|Donald J. Cram]] [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]; '''1952'''; 74(9); 2129-2137 [http://pubs.acs.org/cgi-bin/abstract.cgi/jacsat/1952/74/i09/f_ja01129a001.pdf 摘要] {{Wayback|url=http://pubs.acs.org/cgi-bin/abstract.cgi/jacsat/1952/74/i09/f_ja01129a001.pdf |date=20070929122936 }}</ref>如果这个反应的反应物是光学纯的anti-异构体（指甲基），反应时三元环中间体具有对称轴，故进攻两个环碳得到的产物是等同的，得到光学纯的anti-产物。

